data.name: label1.Text
data.value:
To start, you should open your icontent.cache file, which is located in your "My Documents" folder, under the Battlefield 2142 folder. Other games using IGA ads may store it in other folders.
Make sure you backup your icontent.cache file before opening it with this software.
